<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>处分决定</title>
    <style>
        /* GB/T 9704-2012 党政机关公文格式样式 */
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@400;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@400;500;700&display=swap');

        :root {
            --red-line: #cc0000;
            --text-primary: #000000;
            --text-secondary: #333333;
            --paper-bg: #fffff8;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: #f0f0f0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
            font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', 'SimSun', '宋体', serif;
        }

        .page {
            background: var(--paper-bg);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1100px;
            min-height: 297mm;
            padding: 30mm 40px 30mm 45px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            position: relative;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        /* 发文机关标志 */
        .header-org {
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', 'SimHei', '黑体', sans-serif;
            font-size: 22pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--red-line);
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 8mm;
        }

        /* 文号 */
        .doc-number {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14pt;
            margin-bottom: 6mm;
            font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', '仿宋', 'FangSong', serif;
        }

        .doc-number .year {
            color: var(--red-line);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .doc-number .bracket-open,
        .doc-number .bracket-close {
            color: var(--red-line);
        }

        .doc-number .num {
            color: var(--red-line);
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0 3px;
        }

        /* 红线 */
        .red-line {
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--red-line);
            margin: 5mm 0 8mm 0;
            position: relative;
        }

        .red-line::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -3px;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--red-line);
        }

        .red-line::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -3px;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--red-line);
        }

        /* 标题 */
        .doc-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', '小标宋', 'SimSun', serif;
            font-size: 22pt;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin: 8mm 0 10mm 0;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* 主送机关 */
        .recipient {
            font-size: 14pt;
            margin-bottom: 5mm;
            font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', '仿宋', 'FangSong', serif;
        }

        /* 正文 */
        .doc-body {
            font-size: 14pt;
            font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', '仿宋', 'FangSong', serif;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .doc-body p {
            text-indent: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 3mm;
        }

        .doc-body .no-indent {
            text-indent: 0;
        }

        /* 小标题 */
        .section-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 6mm;
            margin-bottom: 3mm;
            text-indent: 0 !important;
        }

        /* 列表项 */
        .violation-list {
            margin: 3mm 0 3mm 2em;
            padding: 0;
            list-style: none;
            counter-reset: item;
        }

        .violation-list li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 1.5em;
            margin-bottom: 2mm;
            text-indent: 0;
        }

        .violation-list li::before {
            content: counter(item) "、";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            counter-increment: item;
        }

        /* 处分内容 */
        .punishment {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--red-line);
            font-size: 15pt;
        }

        /* 落款区域 */
        .signature-area {
            margin-top: 15mm;
            text-align: right;
            font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', '仿宋', 'FangSong', serif;
            font-size: 14pt;
        }

        .signature-area .org-name {
            margin-bottom: 3mm;
        }

        .signature-area .date {
            margin-top: 2mm;
        }

        /* 附注 */
        .remark {
            margin-top: 10mm;
            font-size: 12pt;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding-top: 3mm;
        }

        /* 版记 */
        .colophon {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20mm;
            left: 28mm;
            right: 26mm;
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            border-top: 1px solid #999;
            padding-top: 3mm;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="page">
        <!-- 发文机关标志 -->
        <div class="header-org">
            {{ group_name }}群管理小组
        </div>

        <!-- 文号 -->
        <div class="doc-number">
            {{ group_name }}
            <span class="bracket-open">〔</span>
            <span class="year">{{ year }}</span>
            <span class="bracket-close">〕</span>
            <span class="num">{{ doc_number }}</span>
            号
        </div>

        <!-- 红线 -->
        <div class="red-line"></div>

        <!-- 标题 -->
        <div class="doc-title">
            关于对 {{ target_nickname }} 同志处分的决定
        </div>

        <!-- 正文 -->
        <div class="doc-body">
            <!-- 受处分人信息 -->
            <p class="no-indent">受处分人：{{ target_nickname }}</p>

            <!-- 一、违纪事实 -->
            <p class="section-title">一、违纪事实</p>
            <p>{{ violation_time }}，在"{{ group_name }}"群内，{{ target_nickname }}同志在与群成员进行日常交流时，{{ violation_background }}，作出如下违纪行为：</p>

            <ul class="violation-list">
                {% for item in violation_details %}
                <li>{{ item }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>

            <!-- 二、处分决定 -->
            <p class="section-title">二、处分决定</p>
            <p>为严肃群内纪律，教育本人并警示他人，经群管理团队研究决定：</p>
            <p>对 <span class="punishment">{{ target_nickname }}</span> 同志给予 <span class="punishment">{{ punishment }}</span> 的处分。</p>

            <!-- 三、整改与申诉要求 -->
            <p class="section-title">三、整改与申诉要求</p>
            {% for req in rectification_requirements %}
            <p>{{ req }}</p>
            {% endfor %}

            <p>本决定自下发之日起生效。</p>
            <p>特此决定。</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 落款 -->
        <div class="signature-area">
            <div class="org-name">{{ group_name }}群管理小组</div>
            <div class="date">{{ date }}</div>
        </div>

        <!-- 版记（可选） -->
        <div class="colophon">
            <span>抄送：全体群成员</span>
            <span>{{ group_name }}群管理小组办公室</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
